      "slides": [
        {
          "menuItem": "Introduction",
          "title": "Express Thanks",
          "body": "<p>Express Thanks is an app designed to help users capture acts of kindness, whether itâ€™s in the form of a gift, experience, or other gesture, and to use that captured information to create a thank you card for the person or people who shared their kindness.  The thank you cards in Express Thanks can be personalized with a photo, personal message and a digital signature.</p><p>The app also allows the user to create a gift list for occasions when you receive many gifts by associating a photo of the gift with the person who gave the gift.  This list can be used within the app to create and send thank you cards digitally through email, text msg. or Facebook, or in the real mail.  If real mail is selected, Express Thanks will print and mail the thank you card to your recipient.  The user can also share this list via email if they are creating a list for someone else who is the guest at the event such as a Bride/Bridesmaid.   That guest can then either use the list to create thank you cards with the app if they have it, or they can use the list to create thank you cards from the Express Thanks web site.</p>",
          "forward": "Dive In!"
        }
      ]
    },
